2.3秒激增至570-690万秒\n   - CheckoutService/PlaceOrder操作延迟从15-16万秒激增至2.2-2.8亿秒\n\n3. **错误传播路径**：CurrencyService故障 → Frontend服务超时 → CheckoutService订单处理失败\n\n4. **错误状态**：大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误，表明上游服务因下游故障而超时。\n\n根因很可能是CurrencyService实例故障，导致依赖货币转换的所有服务链式故障。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "currencyservice-2 is the root cause due to RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded and connection refused errors"}
